By the way I desire you to be patient and stir not, lest we break Glasses: for this operation is very phlegmatick; and your Choler may alter our degree of heat, and so produce
an Empyreuma in our Aquavitae. Stand quietly therefore with expectation (like a Spaniard at the siege of a Piazz •
) and presently your errour shall evaporate, and both our opinions shall dance together in a Limbeck. Marke therefore how true an Analogy there is between Wine and Mans bloud and then tell me whether Hermeticks nurse any Opinions but what are legitimate to reason.

To shew that I am not in choller, therefore, with Methodicall Obstinacy, which Jeeres at Truth, to blinde their Ignorance; 
                     •
                   will drink to them in a Cup of our Hermeticall Claret.
